<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Get Started - Blog Platform</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f8 0%, #8db0d7 100%);
      color: #102a43;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(16, 42, 67, 0.15);
      color: #102a43;
    }
    h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #334e68;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      color: #334e68;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(16, 42, 67, 0.2);
    }
    a:hover {
      background: #243b53;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(16, 42, 67, 0.3);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1>Welcome to our Blog Platform</h1>
    <p>Start sharing your stories and insights. Manage your posts, connect with your audience, and monitor your growth all from one place.</p>
    <a href="/blogs">Get Started</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
